00:20:32.500 --> 00:20:35.390
I took a class in high school
called Industrial Arts.

00:20:35.390 --> 00:20:36.930
It was shop.

00:20:36.930 --> 00:20:39.550
We had it drilled into us, the
eutectic point of soft solder

00:20:39.550 --> 00:20:42.580
is 374 degrees Fahrenheit.

00:20:42.580 --> 00:20:43.960
I will know that
